data.description: Welcome to this charming home; perfect for anyone looking for comfort and convenience. As soon as you walk through the front door, you'll love how the historic features are blended into modern style. The updated kitchen is a chef's dream w/sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and loads of cabinet space, making it an ideal place to whip up delicious meals. The luxurious primary suite is a great place to relax and unwind after a long day and perfect for getting a good night's sleep. The 3rd floor has been turned into 4th bedroom and a bonus room that's just waiting to be used as a home office, playroom, or entertainment area. Minutes from I-670, Franklin Conservatory, and downtown, you'll enjoy making lasting memories in your new home.
